f=Brand Studio/lena/operational/skill/lena-skill-routing.md · p=Lena's routing map. Triggers: `operational/commands/lena-commands.md`. · h2:Where Identity Fits=Lena agent identity spark holds Brand Studio's. *writing* personas humanic-writing's archetypes skill assets, agent identity (deliberate rule-6.1 design). Universal-only principles. · h2:The Writing Pipeline=`voice-guides            (load the brand's voice — the foundation; no guide → create it \· \|                  from real samples before real work) \· copywriting             (STRUCTURE: deterministic formula per content type — \· \|                  AIDA/PAS/BAB/4Ps/4Us/FAB; variants on request) \· email-marketer          (email only: sequence frameworks, cadence, deliverability)` · h2:The Writing Pipeline=piece copy lena produces runs order: · h2:Handoff Rules=**voice-guides everything**: loaded guide governs *how* skills' output sounds; formula keeps structure, voice wins wording., **copywriting nate**: conversion variants (the catalog's "draft variants") hand nate testing; lena writes, nate measures., **email-marketer connector/operator**: sequences designed here, sent configured transport; consent discipline operator's jurisdiction inputs (CASL Canadian businesses stricter skill's framing)., **humanic-writing pulse**: pulse's social drafts run lena's humanic pass (and voice guide) before spark one voice across owned channels., **Voice-breaking requests**: flagged rule quoted; comply logged operator override; repeated overrides amend guide., **Logical layer (pending)**: hook/virality/stickiness formulas await operator-supplied books; until attraction advice flagged reasoning-based rule 0.6. · h2:Cross-Agent Boundaries=Atlas owns text *set* (type, kit); lena owns what *says sounds like*. Weave owns which *story* told; lena words it. Echo consumes lena-quality discipline owns investor documents itself. Kai measures content performance; lena doesn't self-grade. · h2:Precedence="Write structure skill X's type, always humanic-writing. "Fix/humanize humanic-writing directly. "Does sound like us" voice-guides check. Ambiguous ask whether need drafting, structuring, sequencing, humanizing. · f=voice guide voice-guides' creation loop first (or explicitly-labeled voice-neutral draft emergencies). Everything else: skill's clarify-first gate.